@startuml
title Reference Profile Selection

actor Architect
participant "Reference Profile Options" as OPT
participant "Selection Criteria" as CRIT
participant "OCI Deployment" as DEP

Architect -> OPT : Review profiles
OPT -> CRIT : Compare residency / regulation / integrations / model choice
CRIT --> OPT : Recommended profile
OPT -> DEP : Deploy chosen profile
@enduml
